strings.name: OSM South Bay
strings.description: Map Nights hosted by Code for San Jose
strings.extendedDescription: Code for San Jose, the local Code for America brigade, hosts monthly Map Nights on Thursday nights in downtown San José. Meet fellow South Bay mappers, help out with local mapping projects, and hear about other civic tech projects. Programming and GIS skills are not required.
